Global business mogul, Dr Nuel Ojei has lost his immediate younger sibling, Thomas Ojei to the cold hands of death. Please enable JavaScript This is a modal window. Beginning of dialog window. Escape will cancel and close the window. End of dialog window. In a statement by the family of late Chief Sylvester Ojei of Idumu-Osodi, Ogboli quarters, Issele-Uku, Aniocha North Local Government Area of Delta State, late Thomas Uzo Ojei, passed on after a brief illness.Until his demise, late Thomas, the pioneer Technical Sales Manager of Nuel Auto Distributors Ltd, an affiliate of the Nuel Ojei Holdings Ltd conglomerate, was a consummate multi-tentacled business operator, who later founded and successfully managed Tizor Enterprises Nig Ltd to fruition.According to the family, burial arrangement will be announced later.